{"tid":1746111,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普：要不是我照顧香港 香港早就完蛋了","createTime":"2019-11-22T14:47:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T15:04:19.000Z","uid":193217,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ef0b176c09d8bdbedfa3639d779e74bed1fe1651","tid":1746111,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:47:01.000Z","msg":"香港反修例風波愈演愈烈，外界關注美國總統特朗普，會否簽署已在參眾兩院通過的《香港人權與民主法案》（下稱法案）。特朗普周五（22日）受訪時指，未有直接回應會否簽署法案，但稱自己曾警告中國領導人習近平不要派兵到港。<br />\n特朗普接受霍士新聞台節目「Fox &amp; Friends」電話訪問時，被問及會否簽署法案，他態度顯得模棱兩可，未有正面回答，僅稱︰「我們必須與香港同行，但我也與習主席同行。」<br />\n特朗普又聲稱，若不是他要求習近平不要破壞貿易談判，香港早已變成「警察國家」，成千上萬的人已被殺死。特朗普之後指自己要求習近平不要讓一百萬中國士兵進駐香港，以免對貿易談判造成影響，他說︰「要不是我，香港在14分鐘內就已被夷平了。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc2b247cdaae085b4d8f5745c87d842f28648bb","tid":1746111,"uid":193217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:47:24.000Z","msg":"即係話.支共根本想殺晒d香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dc0bf0feb5966d070cb76ac956c9b072e243851","tid":1746111,"uid":15880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:49:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RTthuq1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRTthuq1.jpg&h=296ce150&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4126b577b6d175f7ca4470c7b5bb7e169cc975b4","tid":1746111,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:50:52.000Z","msg":"如果侵侵真係講真<br />\n我真係覺得支共根本想殺晒我地香港人<br />\n所以依家咁多單又突然失蹤.好明顯知道邊個做"},{"pid":"069851397555ccf51cd2181709e0d2b09bef5b52","tid":1746111,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,